title.rendered: DRIVETECH 4X4 HIGH LIFT JACK AND SHOVEL HOLDER MOUNT

content.rendered:
DRIVETECH 4X4 HIGH LIFT JACK AND SHOVEL HOLDER MOUNT

Drivetech 4×4 High Lift Jack and Shovel Holder Mount available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

Features include;

  • Stores your High Lift Jack and shovel safely and securely
  • Allows for easy access
  • Adjustable mounts to suit most makes of roof racks and cages
  • Easy to install and adjust
CLICK HERE to view the full range of products available for your 4×4!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
